TITLE: Implementing Log Node with Both Control Flow and Dataflow Support
DESCRIPTION: Create a Log node class that can receive control flow signals and fetch data from incoming nodes. This demonstrates how to use fetchInputs from DataflowEngine to access data from connected nodes while maintaining control flow.
